commit.message: bump to 6.0.1

fixed: cec-tray didn't start in some cases. set the correct version

closes #522

fixed: v4 compatiblity

only the main lib is fully compatible.
LibCecSharp is initialised differently now
fixed: python wrapper compilation and missing callbacks
fixed: disable deprecated-copy warning on gcc9 for now

unified LibCecSharp and LibCecSharpCore
added: new/missing functions and fields in LibCecSharp
added: firmware can now be upgraded in cec-tray
added: screensaver functionality in cec-tray
added: MuteAudio() command
removed: CanPersistConfiguration() - use CanSaveConfiguration() instead
removed: PersistConfiguration() - SetConfiguration() now stores the cfg in eeprom if available
removed: EnableCallbacks() - use SetCallbacks() and DisableCallbacks()instead
fixed: loading and storing settings in eeprom
fixed: LibCecSharp callbacks could crash
fixed: updating the hdmi port setting or physical address while libCEC is running
fixed: various small robustness improvements and cosmetic changes
fixed: icons are no longer black transperant (and nearly invisible)

bump to 6.0.0
Allows clean upgrades of debian libcec-dev.
